definition: king or monarch/best or strongest of its type/grand/great

sentences.english: Are royal jelly and honey different?
sentences.chinese: 蜂王漿和蜂蜜不一樣嗎？

sentences.english: The healing properties of royal jelly have been known to folk medicine for centuries.
sentences.chinese: 蜂王漿的治療作用已衆所周知，是民間百年藥。

sentences.english: Objective To study the effects of lyophilized royal jelly on immune status in mice.
sentences.chinese: 目的觀察蜂王漿凍乾粉對小鼠免疫功能的影響。

sentences.english: We can not take bee pollen, propolis and royal jelly did not like.
sentences.chinese: 我們不能取蜜蜂的花粉，也沒有蜂膠和蜂王漿之類的。

sentences.english: Color Riche Shine Gelee is the 1st lipstick enriched with Royal Jelly.
sentences.chinese: 紛澤滋潤炫彩晶亮脣膏是第一款富含蜂王漿的脣膏。

sentences.english: It is recorded in Ancient Egyptian history that Cleopatra used royal jelly to help her remain so health and beautiful.
sentences.chinese: 據記錄，古埃及豔后也用蜂王漿來保持健康和美麗。
